of work.%0a%0aNot likely to be labeled a [[NatureVault/PyramidScheme]] unlike limited assets like [[Bitcoin]] although this can be mediated by a [[tail emission]] like [[dogecoin]], [[constant emission]] like [[Grin]], [[Proportonal reward]] like [[Ergon]] and other [[staticcoin]]s, or [[Inflationary reward]] like [[Bitflate]].%0a%0a!!Staked coin derivatives%0a%0aLiquid and coinbase staked eth [[https://cointelegraph.com/news/why-post-merge-ethereum-has-become-obsolete|#]]
